===== 
Carpalx Keyboard - http://mkweb.bcgsc.ca/carpalx/
===== 

Linux
-------- 

This version remaps kbd keys in the kernel using udev.
It is done low level so all ttys + applications will simply work.

For more details, visit
https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Map_scancodes_to_keycodes


Windows
--------

Was created with MS Keyboard Layout Creator 1.0